Package org.postgresql.pljava.model

Interface CatalogObject.Grant

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CatalogObject.CONNECT, CatalogObject.CREATE, CatalogObject.CREATE_TEMP, CatalogObject.DELETE, CatalogObject.Grant.OnAttribute, CatalogObject.Grant.OnClass, CatalogObject.Grant.OnDatabase, CatalogObject.Grant.OnNamespace, CatalogObject.Grant.OnRole, CatalogObject.INSERT, CatalogObject.REFERENCES, CatalogObject.SELECT, CatalogObject.TRIGGER, CatalogObject.TRUNCATE, CatalogObject.UPDATE, CatalogObject.USAGE
    Enclosing interface:
    CatalogObject
    public static interface CatalogObject.Grant
    Interface representing any single Grant (or ACL item), a grant of some set of possible privileges, to some role, granted by some role.

      Subtype of Grant representing the privileges that may be granted on a database.
      static interface  CatalogObject.Grant.OnNamespace
      Subtype of Grant representing the privileges that may be granted on a namespace (or schema).
      static interface  CatalogObject.Grant.OnRole
      Subtype of Grant representing the grants (of membership in, and/or privileges of, other roles) that may be made to a role.
